Package: plsr
Title: Facilitate PLSR on Infared Spectroscopy
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: c(
    person("Emma", "Vejcik", email = "evejcik@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Grace", "Hartley", email = "grace.hartley@gmail.com", role = "aut")
    )
Maintainer: Emma Vejcik <evejcik@gmail.com>
Description: The 'plsr' package works to faciliate Partial Least Squares Regression with infared spectroscopy data. This pacakge is designed to make it easy for geologists to create a model to analyze biogenic silica samples.
